Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:31.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:89485,91529}All right, Lassie.\NI'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:40.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97702,100121}Oh? You're not going by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:41.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100121,101289}I have homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:44.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103041,104417}Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:51.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110506,111883}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111883,113468}You're here for the milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:57.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114260,117430}Thanks for coming,\Nbut I'll have to disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118723,120350}I'm sorry, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120350,122727}I can't give you milk today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:10.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129734,130610}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:24.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142288,144957}Oh? There's no milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:25.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144957,145750}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146417,148753}I thought she'd be okay going alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.71,0:02:32.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150713,152340}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:33.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152340,153424}A message?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153424,154592}What's it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:36.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154592,156761}That they're out of milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158137,160139}But they have that huge cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:44.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160640,164602}What a shame, the soup\Nwon't be as tasty without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:46.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164602,166688}But there's nothing\Nwe can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:48.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166688,168147}Oh? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168815,170066}To Sandy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175530,177657}I suppose the homework\Nwill get done by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183246,186874}Thank goodness, your cow is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186874,188042}She is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:10.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188042,190753}I was scared\Nshe'd died or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:11.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190753,191754}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191754,192964}It's just…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:16.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192964,196718}You've grown up on the\Nmilk from this very cow, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:17.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196718,197677}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:19.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197677,199011}But?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:22.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199178,202014}Moo can't make milk anymore,\Nnot a single drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:23.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202306,203641}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203641,205518}But she's feeding\Nher baby right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:31.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207603,211816}That's just Baby Moo trying her best\Nto squeeze a single drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:35.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211816,215528}I have no choice but to\Nfeed her other cows' milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:38.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215528,218030}Even though her mother's milk\Nis her favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249562,251814}We have no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252565,255985}You know that as well as I do,\Ndon't you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255985,258863}We've tried so many things…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:22.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258863,262992}It's exactly because we tried everything\Nwe have to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:26.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262992,266329}Keep your voice down, honey,\Nor you'll wake up the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:32.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267413,272001}Yes. There is also the matter\Nof what you are going to tell the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:36.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272001,276130}That cow is Sandy's favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:39.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276130,279967}She learned how to\Nmilk cows on Moo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:43.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279967,283179}Yes. I still remember\Nhow happy she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:45.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283179,285348}Enough with this drama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286307,288434}I also worked hard for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288935,290812}No, that is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:54.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290812,294065}Even children have\Nto grow up eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294065,297026}Dad, have you grown\Nso senile it clouds your judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:57.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297026,297819}N-No…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297819,299779}A cow is not a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:02.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299779,302281}If it doesn't bring any profit,\Nwe need to sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302281,304742}If it doesn't give milk,\Nit only means extra expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:07.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305576,307453}Yes… You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:10.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308204,310873}I'll take it to the town\Nfirst thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311207,312208}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:16.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312208,316128}Can it at least wait until Sandy\Ngoes to school? Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319549,322718}What to do? What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359046,360339}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360798,362300}Oh, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362300,363968}Did you hear the news?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:04.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363968,364594}What news?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364594,366804}Apparently there is\Na cattle rustler in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:08.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366804,368306}A cattle rustler?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:19.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377273,379567}There you have it, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:24.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379567,384780}My poor daughter loved the stolen cow so much\Nthat she didn't want to eat at all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386407,389076}How can you be so sure\Nthat it was a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:32.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389076,392747}The barn door was locked from the outside\Nand was wide open this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:34.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392747,394540}What are you suggesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:39.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394540,399253}That the cow magically opened the door\Nfrom the outside and escaped by itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:42.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399253,402006}No, somehow I don't think\Nthat's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402965,404592}This is no laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:49.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404592,409305}How can you be sure that\Nyou're not the next target of this thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:53.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409722,413684}Let me just say, you better have a good proof\Nbefore you call someone a thief,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413684,415311}otherwise you'll just\Nmake a fool of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415311,417271}I speak from experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417271,419774}Whoever it was,\Nthey stole two cows from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:01.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419774,421651}We must catch them\Nand bring them to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421651,424528}Or are you saying we should\Nlet them do what they want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425696,427949}Of course I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:12.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427949,432161}How about we do this,\Nif you find any evidence, let us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432161,433996}Then we'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435206,436999}That's the best option.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.99,0:07:18.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436999,438542}For now it's just finger pointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438542,440670}We can't help him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:21.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440670,441337}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441837,444382}Can I help you in any way, Sandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445132,446884}That looked pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448928,450972}How can my Dad say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450972,452098}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:36.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452098,456852}That I was so sad\Nthat I didn't want to eat and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:39.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456852,459730}When in reality he water\Ntrying to sell off poor Moo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:42.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459730,462149}Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:52.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467571,472410}Under Henry VII's rule, trade and industry\Nwere the backbone of England's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:56.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472410,476914}He firmly believed that war was nothing\Nbut an obstacle to the economic growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:08:01.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476914,481377}That led him to sign the Treaty of\NPerpetual Peace with the Scotland…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486173,487425}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:13.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490386,493681}I don't need anybody's help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:32.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508279,512992}Sandy, if there's something\Nwe can do to help, just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512992,514076}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515661,517121}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:38.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517121,518831}You really want to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:40.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519749,520624}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:44.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520624,524420}We don't want you to be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:47.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524420,527089}Can you keep a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527089,528174}A secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529508,530551}Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530551,531594}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:54.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532470,534972}All right, I'll show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534972,536557}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563209,565252}John… Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:27.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566587,567880}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567880,570758}Promise me that\Nyou won't tell anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572676,574762}Sandy, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:36.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574762,576555}You're acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:39.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576555,579058}You've got to promise me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:40.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579058,580601}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580601,582770}I promise too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:51.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588192,591946}Thanks. Now I can tell you\Nwhat is the big secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:52.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591946,592738}Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602540,603541}It was a cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604166,605334}Can it… Can it be Moo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605334,607586}Wait! Listen to me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:10.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607586,610047}But the thief…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611549,613092}The thief…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615177,616178}…was me all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:17.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616178,617054}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:37.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634363,637992}This is going to end very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:38.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637992,638701}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:42.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639326,642121}But I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644582,646542}What are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647126,649003}I didn't think that far ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650212,653883}I can't think of anything, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:57.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653883,657636}It's better to tell your father, Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:58.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657636,658721}We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:03.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658721,663225}He said that she's useless\Nand that he's going to sell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:06.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664059,666729}So what if we can't come up\Nwith any plan right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:10.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666729,670316}Let's just raise her ourselves!\NUntil we think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:12.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670316,672067}What if we can't think of anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:16.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672067,676071}We will. We just will, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676071,677239}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:17.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677239,677948}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678866,680534}Tell them, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683704,685372}The weather is so good today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:29.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687541,689501}It's so nice to be off duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689501,692046}I can drink as much as I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695216,696717}– Am I doing this right?\N– Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:39.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696717,699803}Maybe she'll give milk again\Nif we graze her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:42.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699803,702223}It's possible, in theory…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702223,705017}But we tried it already\Nso many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:46.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705017,706477}We've just gotta try harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:47.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706477,707811}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:06.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724411,726705}What? You're sure it was a cow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:09.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726705,729041}Yes, I also heard some people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730584,731543}Alright then!
Comment: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:14.25,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:734255,734255}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738008,739051}There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740135,742554}This is an undeniable lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:25.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742554,745057}Bansen will take us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747685,749520}Fine by me, but, you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749520,750896}This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750896,752147}We've got to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:33.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752147,753857}What? Did I hear you right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753857,755734}You're not sure where it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:39.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755734,759571}Oh, I was a little bit\Ndrunk at the time…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:41.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760155,761198}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761198,763409}Why don't we figure it on our way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763409,764952}Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764952,767162}Now's our only chance\Nto move Moo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767162,768038}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773335,774670}Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776130,777047}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777047,778799}I'd like to ask you for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:04.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780759,784305}I'd like you and your dog\Nto go with Bansen and us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785306,787308}How does that sound?\NAny objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:08.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787725,788934}That's our best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:10.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788934,790311}Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793897,795566}Sandy! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795566,797860}If we don't hurry up,\Nthey will get to her before us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798193,799320}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799320,802072}We must catch the thief\Nbefore he escapes us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:24.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802072,804074}Is there really a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:26.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804074,806368}This is getting weirder\Nby the minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:29.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806535,809496}Hey, all of you!\NCan't you go faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:31.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809496,811498}Colin! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817463,819298}I'm sorry, Moo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:41.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819298,821508}We must take you\Nsomewhere else again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821508,823469}Please, be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826221,827222}Moo…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:58.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836357,838442}This is the right way, right?\NYou're sure of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838442,839902}Yes. I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:04.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843781,844656}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:08.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845699,848327}We're not going to let them\Nhave their way, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:14.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852289,854208}What's the matter, Moo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854208,856085}She won't move…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861298,863300}Okay, listen close, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863300,865010}We're going to lure them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:25.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865010,865886}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866303,867721}Looks like they lost something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:28.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867721,868889}Think it belongs to the thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869598,871266}No, no, that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872351,874103}That's actually mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:36.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874103,876730}I must've dropped it\Nhere yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876730,879858}You lost such an important thing?\NAnd you call yourself a drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:44.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881151,884822}This is not the time to laugh.\NFocus on the matter at hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884822,886240}Are we close?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886240,887366}I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:51.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888283,891078}Now, where to…\NWas it this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891078,892871}No, maybe it was that way…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:54.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893580,894623}Which was it…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:55.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894623,895374}This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895833,898836}Looks like Lassie\Npicked up some scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898836,900379}Right, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:03.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901588,903048}Well done, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:903048,904216}This way, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906927,908637}They're going a different way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909263,911140}John did something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911140,912891}Now's our chance. Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913058,915894}Please, move, Moo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927322,929158}Lassie, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:32.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929158,932077}We have to lead them\Nas far away as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938250,939168}Moo…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:40.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939168,940461}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940461,942921}If we stay here,\Nmy father will find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947801,949761}Don't you get it, Moo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:52.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949761,952431}Don't you care what's going\Nto happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:56.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952890,956435}As expected,\Nshe doesn't understand us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956435,958937}That's not true!\NRight, Moo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:15:59.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958937,959938}Baby Moo…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965819,967821}Hey, if we go this way…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967821,969406}Jon! Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969406,970157}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:13.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970866,973368}There is no point in going further.\NThere is no way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973368,974203}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981502,983378}I don't know who the thief is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:26.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983378,986298}but they couldn't move\Nthe cows over that river.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:30.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988175,990928}Isn't it better to go back\Nto where we were before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:31.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990928,991637}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:33.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992554,993555}John…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:34.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994139,994932}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007194,1008195}This way?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:50.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009029,1010447}Follow me, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:56.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014117,1016870}We can't go this way, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017246,1018413}And why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018413,1020999}The previous path was a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025629,1027965}Don't go this way, Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:11.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031260,1031969}Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039268,1041853}Oh? What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041853,1043855}Amazing…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044606,1046441}Wild grapes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:35.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050779,1055242}There's so much.\NThey'll make a splendid wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:41.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056451,1061248}Leave the cow and the milk.\NLook at this treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062082,1063500}Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063500,1064751}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072968,1074886}She's following,\Nshe's following!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074886,1076805}We should've done so\Nright from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082894,1084313}Stop it, Moo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084313,1085772}We have to hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:07.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086148,1087232}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:10.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090110,1090819}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:12.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091820,1092696}Moo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092696,1094156}Sir, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095282,1096241}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:30.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107502,1110589}Do you even understand\Nwhat you have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:35.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111882,1115302}I just wanted…\NI just wanted to save Moo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115302,1117262}I don't want you to sell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118096,1119806}Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:43.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119806,1123477}Do you think that I'm selling her\Nbecause I want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:48.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124019,1128482}Moo helped our farm a great deal.\NIt's difficult for me to let go of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128982,1130359}Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131151,1132861}I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132861,1135447}If you don't want to sell her,\Njust don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135447,1136907}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137866,1139743}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139743,1141703}I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147042,1148585}Sandy…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155425,1158637}Sir, is there any way\Nfor us to save Moo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158637,1160972}You think you're saving her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:24.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160972,1164393}What about you, kids?\NYou want the baby to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:31.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168271,1171566}It is better to sell her\Nfor Baby Moo's sake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:36.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171566,1176488}When she's near her mother, she does not\Nwant to drink milk from other cows at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:39.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176863,1179741}But is there nothing we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179741,1181993}That's just a lot.\NThat's just too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:07.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205976,1207060}Hey, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:11.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208103,1211690}Same as usual.\NThe milk doesn't come out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:17.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216236,1217404}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217404,1219281}You're worried\Nabout her too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:25.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222993,1225495}Let's not stand around\Nhere crying like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227247,1228290}Sandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232419,1233462}Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:38.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237966,1238967}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:43.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242596,1243972}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:45.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243972,1245098}You won't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245098,1247392}It's Moo! She gave milk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250604,1253482}What's this?\NWhy's everyone in such a rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254357,1255776}I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267078,1268330}You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:11.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268330,1271124}I was looking everywhere\Nfor these flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:16.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271124,1276004}When Sandy's father was born, we made her\Neat them until her condition improved, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:18.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276630,1278048}Is that a medicinal plant?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278048,1279090}You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:19.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279090,1279966}Moo…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:25.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282552,1285055}You knew that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:28.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287098,1288683}Are you happy, Sandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289476,1291269}Listen, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:35.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291269,1295941}Next time she doesn't give milk,\Njust leave it to me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:37.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296650,1297901}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:40.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299569,1300695}Father…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301863,1303532}I'm sorry.
